ass=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3615576\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3615576\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Apr 20, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104rdf1665702687207.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rdf1665702687207.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rdf1665702687207.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"rdf1665702687207\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Height of each row in the Grid widget, in character cells or pixels. Default value is <code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code> (character cell).\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rdf1665702687207__p_d106766e1_d106767e1_d106768e1\">RowHeight<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code><var class=\"keyword varname\">NumberOfCells</var> |\n        <var class=\"keyword varname\">NumberOfPixels</var><code class=\"ph codeph\">px</code><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code></p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"rdf1665702687207__table_d12599e1_d12600e1_d12601e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rdf1665702687207__table_d12599e1_d12600e1_d12601e1__entry__1\">Value </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rdf1665702687207__table_d12599e1_d12600e1_d12601e1__entry__2\">Description </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdf1665702687207__table_d12599e1_d12600e1_d12601e1__entry__1\">&gt;= <code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdf1665702687207__table_d12599e1_d12600e1_d12601e1__entry__2\">Number of cells; default is <code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdf1665702687207__table_d12599e1_d12600e1_d12601e1__entry__1\">&gt;= <code class=\"ph codeph\">0px</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdf1665702687207__table_d12599e1_d12600e1_d12601e1__entry__2\">Number of pixels </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rdf1665702687207__section_s2t_pyj_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d603749e121\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rdf1665702687207__p_d106772e1_d106773e1_d106774e1\">The <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Row Height</span> defines the\n        height of all rows in the Grid widget. To set the row size of the current occurrence, use\n          <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Current Occurrence Row Size</span>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rdf1665702687207__p_d106775e1_d106776e1_d106777e1\">If the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Row Height</span> property is\n        not set, the height of the rows is determined by the largest font that is used in the\n        row.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rdf1665702687207__p_d106778e1_d106779e1_d106780e1\">If the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Row Height</span> property is\n        set, changing the font of the fields in the grid does not change the height of the rows.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rdf1665702687207__p_d106781e1_d106782e1_d106783e1\">End users can use the mouse to make a row higher. When\n        you set the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Row Height</span> property you will override that.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rdf1665702687207__section_orc_ryj_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d603749e154\">Setting Row Height</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"rdf1665702687207__ul_epk_tyj_zwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rdf1665702687207__li_d42203e1_d42204e1_d42205e1\">When the row height is specified in cells, the height\n          is based on the Uniface Font 0, as specified by the Font0 setting in the\n            <span class=\"ph filepath\">.ini</span> file. <p class=\"p\" id=\"rdf1665702687207__p_d106787e1_d106788e1_d106789e1\">To specify the\n            row height in cells, you must set an integer for the number of cells. For\n            example:</p><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"rdf1665702687207__pre_hpk_tyj_zwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$entityproperties(ORDER_LINES)=\"rowheight=2\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div><p class=\"p\" id=\"rdf1665702687207__p_d106790e1_d106791e1_d106792e1\">Setting the row height to <code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code> resets\n            the row height to its initial value.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rdf1665702687207__li_d42206e1_d42207e1_d42208e1\">When the row height is specified in pixels, the\n          minimum height is the height of a cell in Font 0. If you specify a smaller value, it is\n          ignored. <p class=\"p\" id=\"rdf1665702687207__p_d106793e1_d106794e1_d106795e1\">To specify the row height in pixels, add\n              <code class=\"ph codeph\">px</code> after the value. For\n            example:</p><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"rdf1665702687207__pre_jpk_tyj_zwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$entityproperties(ORDER_LINES)=\"rowheight=20px\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div><p class=\"p\" id=\"rdf1665702687207__p_d106796e1_d106797e1_d106798e1\">Setting the row height to <code class=\"ph codeph\">0px</code>\n            resets the row height to its initial value.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"note tip note_tip\" id=\"rdf1665702687207__note_kpk_tyj_zwb\"><span class=\"note__title\">Tip:</span> You can query the Font 0 cell height\n      in pixels using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$cellinfo</span>.</div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rdf1665702687207__p_d106799e1_d106800e1_d106801e1\">Removing the rowheight property from the property\n        string (as set in the <span class=\"ph filepath\">.ini</span> file, or using\n          <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$entityproperties</span>) resets the height of the rows to the initial\n        height.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rdf1665702687207__p_d106802e1_d106803e1_d106804e1\">Setting the property to an invalid value also resets\n        the row height to the initial value.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rdf1665702687207__section_um1_zyj_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d603749e213\">Applies to</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"clg1695282025414.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/clg1695282025414.html\" title=\"The egrid widget displays data in a tabular format, in which the rows are occurrences of an entity and the columns are fields. It is an entity-level widget that is only applicable to form components.\">egrid (Grid)</a></p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/han1665702687338.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Current Occurrence Row Height ( CurOccRowHeight)</a><p>Row height of the current occurrence in the Grid widget, in character cells or pixels. Default value is 1 (character cell).</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dzl1665703006803.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$cellinfo</a><p>Get an associative list with the dimensions of a character cell in pixels.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tlm1665702687704.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$entityproperties</a><p>Return or set the current representation properties of an entity.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615576\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615576\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Row Height (RowHeight) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Apr 20, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Height of each row in the Grid widget, in character cells or pixels. Default value is 1 (character cell). RowHeight = \" NumberOfCells | NumberOfPixels px \" Value Description >= 0 Number of cells; default is 1 >= 0px Number of pixels Description The Row Height defines the height of all rows in the Grid widget. To set the row size of the current occurrence, use Current Occurrence Row Size . If the Row Height property is not set, the height of the rows is determined by the largest font that is used in the row. If the Row Height property is set, changing the font of the fields in the grid does not change the height of the rows. End users can use the mouse to make a row higher. When you set the Row Height property you will override that. Setting Row Height When the row height is specified in cells, the height is based on the Uniface Font 0, as specified by the Font0 setting in the .ini file. To specify the row height in cells, you must set an integer for the number of cells. For example: $entityproperties(ORDER_LINES)=\"rowheight=2\" Copy Setting the row height to 0 resets the row height to its initial value. When the row height is specified in pixels, the minimum height is the height of a cell in Font 0. If you specify a smaller value, it is ignored. To specify the row height in pixels, add px after the value. For example: $entityproperties(ORDER_LINES)=\"rowheight=20px\" Copy Setting the row height to 0px resets the row height to its initial value. Tip: You can query the Font 0 cell height in pixels using $cellinfo . Removing the rowheight property from the property string (as set in the .ini file, or using $entityproperties ) resets the height of the rows to the initial height. Setting the property to an invalid value also resets the row height to the initial value. Applies to egrid (Grid) Related Links Current Occurrence Row Height ( CurOccRowHeight) Row height of the current occurrence in the Grid widget, in character cells or pixels. Default value is 1 (character cell). $cellinfo Get an associative list with the dimensions of a character cell in pixels. $entityproperties Return or set the current representation properties of an entity. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}